OL,3,CStorm Chandra and the growing flood
OL,4,Crisk facing the UK
OL,6,FThis is a crucial point often missed
OL,7,Fin discussions around flooding on this
OL,8,Fscale; it is rarely the result of a
OL,9,Fsingle day of rain.
OL,11,FInstead, these events are the result
OL,12,Fof a gradual build-up, where soils
OL,13,Fbecome fully saturated, and rivers
OL,14,Fstart from an already elevated level.
OL,16,FHow wet has it been so far this season?
OL,18,FRainfall this winter has been
OL,19,Fpersistently above average for many
OL,20,Fparts of the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
