OL,4,Crisk facing the UK
OL,6,FUnsurprisingly, this is particularly
OL,7,Ftrue for regions currently affected by
OL,8,Fflooding.
OL,10,FFor example, rainfall in December
OL,11,Freached 131% of the average across the
OL,12,Fsouth-west of England and south Wales;
OL,13,Ffollowed by 135% of the average in the
OL,14,Fsame area the following month, with
OL,15,Fstill a few days to go until the end
OL,16,Fof the month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
