OL,3,CStorm Chandra and the growing flood
OL,4,Crisk facing the UK
OL,6,FThe picture is similar across Northern
OL,7,FIreland, where the January rainfall
OL,8,Ffigure is already 1.5 times the
OL,9,Fnormal, and some observation sites
OL,10,Fhave reported their wettest days on
OL,11,Frecord as Storm Chandra moved through.
OL,13,FWith this amount of rain falling in
OL,14,Fjust the last eight weeks, the
OL,15,Fsituation was already precarious.
OL,17,FSo what actually happened on Tuesday
OL,18,Fwhen Storm Chandra arrived?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
