OL,3,CStorm Chandra and the growing flood
OL,4,Crisk facing the UK
OL,6,FWhen rainfall falls onto saturated
OL,7,Fground, it runs straight into rivers
OL,8,Frather than soaking into the soil.
OL,10,FWith river levels themselves already
OL,11,Fhigh and the ground unable to absorb
OL,12,Fany more moisture, this led to rivers
OL,13,Fbreaching and surface water flooding
OL,14,Fin both rural and urban areas, as
OL,15,Fdrains too struggled to cope with the
OL,16,Fvolume of runoff.
