OL,3,CStorm Chandra and the growing flood
OL,4,Crisk facing the UK
OL,6,FThe UK has become steadily wetter
OL,7,Fsince the 1980s, with more intense
OL,8,Frainfall events, particularly during
OL,9,Fautumn and winter.
OL,11,FAt the same time, sea levels around
OL,12,Fthe UK continue to rise, making it
OL,13,Fharder for rivers to drain during
OL,14,Fperiods of high tide and also
OL,15,Fworsening the impact of storm surges.
OL,17,FWhat can we learn from this?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
