OL,3,CStorm Chandra and the growing flood
OL,4,Crisk facing the UK
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency warns that
OL,7,Fwithout adaptation, the number of
OL,8,Fproperties at risk of flooding will
OL,9,Fcontinue to rise.
OL,11,FIts long-term strategy focuses not
OL,12,Fjust on flood defences, but on working
OL,13,Fwith natural processes ` restoring
OL,14,Ffloodplains, slowing river flows
OL,15,Fupstream, and improving land
OL,16,Fmanagement to help soils retain water
OL,17,Ffor longer.
OL,19,FStorm Chandra is a reminder that
OL,20,Fflooding is not an isolated hazard but
OL,21,Fpart of a wider climate picture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
