OL,3,CStorm Chandra and the growing flood
OL,4,Crisk facing the UK
OL,6,FAs rainfall patterns shift and very
OL,7,Fwet winters become more common, the
OL,8,Fchallenge is not just predicting
OL,9,Fstorms more accurately, but adapting
OL,10,Fhow and where we live to reduce their
OL,11,Fimpact.
OL,13,FFlooding has always been part of the
OL,14,FUK's weather story.
OL,16,FBut as the Met Office and Environment
OL,17,FAgency both warn, climate change is
OL,18,Ftipping the balance ` making events
OL,19,Flike those seen during Storm Chandra
OL,20,Fmore likely in the years to come.
